None of you know blackpilling... I know stories so filthy you can't even imagine.

I know a boy whose rich psychologist mother bought him a session with a prostitute for his 18th birthday because he was a virgin and "lacked experience". And I know worse humiliation, worse filth.

I know of a highschool student who brought a girl he liked to an outta town house party, with the intention to fuck her. She was a virgin. He too. They were drinking and pretending to have fun, he lacked the courage to take her to a room and do what he wanted, so he kept drinking

She ended up losing her virginity next to his sleeping body, in a threesome with his two best friends. They told him what happened in the morning, he forgave them. She ended up becoming a quite literal whore, messaging random men from town, going from apartment to apartment

I know of a boy who was turned into a homosexual through excessive bullying. He was a frail, small HS guy, not many friends. He mentioned to a fat girl he trusted, a "friend" of his, that he was insecure about his small penis. She told about it to everyone in the school.

Another classmate, a prostitute (she started after her father took her phone away as punishment and she fucked an old guy for money for a new one) decided to absolutely ruin him through a horrifying prank. She pretended to be into him, and took the poor boy on a mock "date"...

Yes, it was very small. She proceeded to laugh and kick him out of the apartment, he was too weak to do anything. Next day at school everyone had seen his micropenis, and proceeded to mecilessly mock him. They even sent the pic to his parents. Now he wears makeup and dates gays.

And I know of far, far worse filth. Stories that would make this thread look wholesome. Stories of rape, abuse, mockery. And this is all from a single school in a small town in /trad/ Eastern Europe. Where, as twitter knows, girls are shy and nice, and love being called pretty!

Ofc, I post this not to depress you. Just to illustrate that you dont have it as bad as you think you do. Life always was rotten, and it will be so until the End of days. Such are the rules of our world. And so it shall be. Do not despair. Do not let the world poison you.

We routinely make ourselves sadder, share blackpilling articles, weep, nag. All of this is useless, masturbatory.

Let us instead try to make ourselves pure, to counterattack this world, to seize it for Good. It is good to gaze at the Void, as Evolist says, but not for too long.

If you live good, pious lifes and cultivate inner and outer strength, none of this can happen to you.

Remember that no matter what filth you are in, you can always be saved. This world is rotten, but you do not belong to it.

This december be positive, do good deeds, and smile.
